WEBVTT

00:09:29.625 --> 00:09:32.418
If you ask people, "Has global
poverty gone up or down?"

00:09:32.442 --> 00:09:34.799
they give the wrong answer,
they say it's gone up.

00:09:34.823 --> 00:09:39.945
CA: OK, so what I'd love to do
is to dig into a few more of your examples

00:09:39.969 --> 00:09:42.507
of where you believe
progress has been made.

00:09:42.531 --> 00:09:47.097
You've presented compelling stats
about life span, health,

00:09:47.121 --> 00:09:51.322
education, safety
and several other things,

00:09:51.346 --> 00:09:54.778
all of which show shocking,
stunning progress

00:09:54.802 --> 00:09:56.683
over the last few hundred years.

00:09:56.707 --> 00:09:59.556
What other aspects of progress
are notable to you?